    <script type="application/ld+json">
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
        "name": "Parseur",
        "url": "https://parseur.com",
        "operatingSystem": "Web Browser",
        "applicationCategory": "BusinessApplication",
        "aggregateRating": { "@type": "AggregateRating", "bestRating": 5, "ratingValue": "4.90", "reviewCount": 60, "worstRating": 4 },
        "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "price": "0", "priceCurrency": "USD" }
      }
    </script>
    
    
    <script type="application/ld+json">
        { "@context": "https://schema.org",
          "@type": "FAQPage",
          "mainEntity": [{ "@type": "Question",
                "name": "How long does it take to get started?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                  "@type": "Answer",
                  "text": "<p>Most teams configure their first mailbox and begin extracting data within minutes. There&#39;s no model training or dataset preparation required. You define your fields and start sending documents.</p>"
                }
              },{ "@type": "Question",
                "name": "Do I need a developer to use Parseur?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                  "@type": "Answer",
                  "text": "<p>No. Non-technical teams can configure extraction and exports directly in the web app. If you need deeper integration, developers can use the API to automate everything programmatically.</p>"
                }
              },{ "@type": "Question",
                "name": "What types of documents can Parseur handle?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                  "@type": "Answer",
                  "text": "<p>Parseur works with emails, PDFs, scanned documents, images, spreadsheets, and more formats across many industries and use cases.</p>"
                }
              },{ "@type": "Question",
                "name": "What happens when document formats change?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                  "@type": "Answer",
                  "text": "<p>Because extraction is instruction-based rather than trained on large sample datasets, Parseur adapts more easily to layout changes. You can also refine fields or rules at any time without retraining a model.</p>"
                }
              },{ "@type": "Question",
                "name": "How does data retention work?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                  "@type": "Answer",
                  "text": "<p>You decide how long your data remains stored in Parseur. Retention settings are customizable per mailbox, so you stay in control of how your documents are handled.</p>"
                }
              },{ "@type": "Question",
                "name": "Is Parseur secure?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                  "@type": "Answer",
                  "text": "<p>Parseur follows industry best security practices and undergoes regular third-party security testing. We are currently completing SOC 2 Type II and HIPAA compliance programs. Customer data is never reused to train our AI models and is never sold.</p>"
                }
              },{ "@type": "Question",
                "name": "How does Parseur handle data privacy and regulations?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                  "@type": "Answer",
                  "text": "<p>Parseur is EU-hosted and aligned with major data protection regulations including EU GDPR, UK GDPR, California CCPA/CPRA, and Singapore PDPA. Data residency is maintained in the EU, and customers control their data retention settings.</p>"
                }
              },{ "@type": "Question",
                "name": "Do I need a credit card to try Parseur?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                  "@type": "Answer",
                  "text": "<p>No. You can sign up and start extracting data for free without entering any payment information. Parseur includes a free tier so you can test it with your own documents before committing.</p>"
                }
              },{ "@type": "Question",
                "name": "Can I upgrade, downgrade, or cancel at any time?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                  "@type": "Answer",
                  "text": "<p>Yes. All plan changes are self-service. You can upgrade, downgrade, or cancel directly from your account settings at any time, no sales calls or hoops required.</p>"
                }
              },{ "@type": "Question",
                "name": "Can Parseur handle high volumes or business-critical workflows?",
                "acceptedAnswer": {
                  "@type": "Answer",
                  "text": "<p>Yes. Parseur is built for production use, with uptime consistently above 99.9% and systems designed for reliability and redundancy. Many teams rely on it for real-time document flows where delays are not acceptable.</p>"
                }
              }]
        }
      </script>
    
