              <p class="-indent-1.5">"We started Parseur because too many smart teams were wasting hours copying data from documents into the systems that actually run their business.
</p>
            
          
            
              <p>That never made sense to us.</p>
            
          
            
              <p>We believe time is precious, and repetitive work should be automated. Not with fragile setups or long consulting projects, but with reliable systems that just work.
</p>
            
          
            
              <p>We build Parseur the same way we believe automation should work: simple, repeatable, reliable, and built to last. We focus on long-term trust, strong privacy foundations, and features that help our entire user base, not one-off custom work.
</p>
            
          
            
              <p>When repetitive work disappears, your team gets its time back to focus on work that actually moves the business forward."
</p>
            
          
        </div>
